N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 196.14 - Retention of examination papers

State Regulations

All persons and organizations conducting approved courses
of study shall retain examination papers for persons attending for a period of
two years after the completion thereof, and such papers shall at all time
during such period be available for inspection by duly authorized
representatives of the department. Notes
